message.raw: Made a change that will hopefully allow time values greater than 28 seconds, up to limit of fifty-something seconds, which is the actual limit of the hardware. I was using a signed integer for the timepoints rather than an unsigned one, which lead to a factor of two difference in the maximum valuee.
